.C.|Bandung United]] until 31 December 2020}}\n{{Fs player|no=30|nat=IDN|pos=GK|name=[[Aqil Savik]]|other=at [[Bandung United F.C.|Bandung United]] until 31 December 2020}}\n{{Fs player|no=98|nat=IDN|pos=FW|name=[[Wildan Ramdhani]]|other=at [[Bandung United F.C.|Bandung United]] until 31 December 2020}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n=== Reserves players and Academy ===\n''For further information: [[Persib Bandung U-21]]''\n\n''For further information: [[Persib Bandung U-19]]''\n\n== Club officials ==\n\n=== Coaching staff ===\n{{updated|1 Januari 2020.}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.persib.co.id/persib/informasi-club/official.aspx|title=Informasi klub official|publisher=|accessdate=22 September 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.inilahkoran.com/berita/persib/56525/fisioterapis-persib-asal-cimahi|title=Fisioterapis Persib Asal Cimahi|publisher=|accessdate=28 February 2017}}</ref>\n<!-- --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  -- Do NOT add new players before their signing is officially announced by the club\n  -- and do NOT assign unreferenced squad numbers as well.\n  -- Do NOT create articles for new player until they make either their League or Cup debut, and do not add red wikilinks to these players as it prevents the creation of articles by people who don't understand the WP:FOOTY notability guidelines\n  \u2013 Players with international caps should NOT be bolded \u2013 as per Wikipedia:WikiProject_Football/Clubs\n  \u2013 This is Wikipedia, not a football gazette.\n  \u2013 Any unconfirmed and unsourced signing/transfer will be reverted.\n  \u2013 Thanks in advance.\n  --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- -->\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:blue; color:white; border:2px solid grey;\" scope=\"col\"|Position\n! style=\"background:blue; color:white; border:2px solid grey;\" scope=\"col\"|Name\n\n|-\n| Manager || {{Flagicon|NED}} [[Robert Alberts]]\n|-\n| Assistant Coach ||  {{Flagicon|IDN}} [[Budiman Yunus]]\n|-\n| Goalkeeping Coach || {{Flagicon|BRA}} [[:id:Luizinho passos|Luizinho passos]]\n|-\n| Fitness Coach || {{Flagicon|IDN}} [[:id:Yaya Sunarya|Yaya Sunarya]]\n|-\n| Doctor || {{Flagicon|IDN}} [[:id:Mohammad Raffi Ghani|Mohammad Raffi Ghani]] \n|-\n| Physioterapist || {{Flagicon|IDN}} [[:id:Benidektus Adi Prianto|Benidektus Adi Prianto]] \n|-\n| General Secretary || {{Flagicon|IDN}} Yudiana\n|}\n\n=== Head Coach history ===\n''Head Coach by years (1982\u2013present)''\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!style=\"background:Blue; color:white;\"|Name\n!style=\"background:Blue; color:white;\"|From\n!style=\"background:Blue; color:white;\"|To\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Omo Suratmo\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1982\n| align=center| 1983\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Ade Dana\n| align=center| 1984\n| align=center| 1985\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Nandar Iskandar\n| align=center| 1985\n| align=center|1986\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Ade Dana\n| align=center| 1989\n| align=center| 1990\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Indra Thohir\n| align=center| 1993\n| align=center| 1995\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Risnandar Soendoro\n| align=center| 1995\n| align=center| 1996\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} M. Suryamin\n| align=center| 1998\n| align=center| 2000\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Indra Thohir\n| align=center| 2000\n| align=center| 2000\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Deny Syamsudin\n| align=center| 2001\n| align=center| 2002\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Poland}} Marek Andrzej \u015aledzianowski\n| align=center| 2003\n| align=center| 2003\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Chile}} Juan Antonio P\u00e1ez\n| align=center| 2003\n| align=center| 2005\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Indra Thohir\n| align=center| 2005\n| align=center| 2006\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} Risnandar Soendoro\n| align=center| 2006\n| align=center| 2006\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Moldova}} {{flagicon|Indonesia}}[[Arcan Iurie]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2006