a | publisher = Tatali Publishing | date = March 2015 | language = Indonesian | location = Bandung | pages = 200  | isbn = 978-602-96971-2-4}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://onesearch.perpusnas.go.id/Record/IOS1-INLIS000000000668385 |title=Musim sang juara : penuntasan misi 19 tahun penuntasan misi 19 tahun / |publisher=Perpusnas.go.id |language=En}}</ref>\n*{{Cite book | last = Ryza | first = Dio | title = Mengenal dan Mewarnai Pemain Sepak Bola Persib Bandung | publisher = Zikrul Hakim | date = 2011 | language = English, Indonesian| location = Jakarta | pages = 24  | isbn = 978-979-063-240-0}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://onesearch.perpusnas.go.id/Record/IOS1-INLIS000000000583125|title= Mengenal dan Mewarnai Pemain Sepak Bola Persib Bandung|publisher=Perpusnas.go.id|language=En}}</ref>\n*{{Cite book | last = Ayati  | first = Nur | title = Liga Indonesia: Persija vs Persib | publisher = Elex Media Komputindo | date = 2010 | language = Indonesian | location = Jakarta | pages = 24  | isbn = 978-979-27-7425-2}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://onesearch.perpusnas.go.id/Record/IOS1-INLIS000000000389524 |title=Liga Indonesia: Persija vs Persib |publisher=Perpusnas.go.id|language=En}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons category|Persib Bandung}}\n* {{Official website|http://www.persib.co.id}} {{in lang|id|en}}\n* [http://www.clubwebsite.co.uk/persibworld/ Unofficial website] {{in lang|en}}\n* [http://fifa.com/world-match-centre/clubs/club=indonesia-persib-2147482093/index.html Persib Bandung] on [[FIFA]]\n* [http://www.ligaindonesia.co.id/index.php/klub/PERSIB-11/ Persib Bandung] on [[Liga Indonesia]]\n* [http://www.indonesiansc.com/klub/persib-bandung/ Persib Bandung] on [[Indonesia Soccer Championship]]\n\n{{Persib Bandung}}\n{{Football clubs in Indonesia}}\n{{Indonesia Super League champions|state=collapsed}}\n{{Liga Indonesia Premier Division champions|state=autocollapse}}\n{{Indonesia Super League}}\n\n[[Category:Persib Bandung]]\n[[Ca